data.description: Come check out this beautiful 2 story home nestled in the Vine Creek subdivision in Pflugerville! The family room is open to the stunning kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances, light granite countertops with dark brown finished cabinets and an oversized center island that serves as a breakfast bar! All bedrooms are located upstairs. Upstairs you will find a second family room and 3 additional bedrooms. Primary bedroom includes an en-suite and a large walk in closet! Covered patio and a nice sized fenced in backyard! Located a minutes from the community clubhouse, playground, and pool. Convienient to Weiss Ln and minutes from Cele Middle School. Don't miss this opportunity! Contact me for more information!
